:: Spa [nobr location]
<<set $gamelocation to "Spa">>

You see a lavish spa for relaxation. Included is a steam room, hot tub, and private massage room.

<br>
Unfortunately a astral barrier blocks the way forward, with the words "THIS AREA IS UNDER CONSTRUCTION"
